## üë®‚Äçüíª Development

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.13+
- [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) package manager

### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/grota/changedetection-tui.git
cd changedetection-tui

# Install dependencies
uv sync --dev

# Run from venv
uv run cdtui

# Run in development mode
uv run textual console -x SYSTEM  -x WORKER -x DEBUG -x EVENT
# Run connecting to textual's console
uv run textual run --dev .venv/bin/cdtui
```

### Development Tools

```bash
# Install precommits (ruff linting and formatting)
uv run pre-commit install

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Format code
uv run ruff format .

# Lint code
uv run ruff check .
```

### üìÇ Project Structure

```
src/changedetection_tui/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ __main__.py       # CLI entry point
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ app.py            # Main application
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main_screen.py    # Main screen layout
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ dashboard/        # Dashboard components
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ settings/         # Settings management
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ utils.py          # Utility functions
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ tui.scss          # Textual CSS styling
```

